products.description: Canvas Leather finishes Round tip Laceup Saint Laurent logo printed Genuine leather interior Padded ankle Rubber sole with dirty effect Made in Italy Thanks to its founder, innovator and trend precursor, the iconic French Maison of Saint Laurent marks a chapter of social changes that have revolutionized the world of fashion. The current creative director Anthony Vaccarello reworks the codes of bourgeois aesthetics so dear to Monsieur Yves Saint Laurent and sets the set of the new collection between apocalyptic beaches, volcanic rocks and the glaciers of Iceland. An icy climate overwhelmed by a silver wind, a glam aesthetic with laminated bodies paired with tweed mini skirts and jackets, skinny silhouettes and short lengths.
